nodes.text: April Stewart is a voice actress credited as providing additional voices to Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic and Star Wars: The Old Republic. She is famous for her role as Wendy Testaburger, among several others, on South Park. She was born on February 8, 1968 in Truckee, California in the United States of America.
